{"tid":2294390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台查利君雅 只看投訴不理讚賞","createTime":"2020-11-21T03:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T03:51:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f52fd7d08ce8082d45b02aa3452e003dc4633886","tid":2294390,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/TAYWEZICCNFILANN5OAOUW7OWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FTAYWEZICCNFILANN5OAOUW7OWU%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=1fd32570\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FTAYWEZICCNFILANN5OAOUW7OWU%2F&h=989bf3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/TAYWEZICCNFILANN5OAOUW7OWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港台查利君雅 只看投訴不理讚賞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W82V2bRvYMuSJv1lEzntsvVrqDY=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KAS2VDV42ZCVRPXE5ZYQO6BYAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW82V2bRvYMuSJv1lEzntsvVrqDY%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKAS2VDV42ZCVRPXE5ZYQO6BYAY.jpg&h=30befd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利君雅<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港台助理節目主任利君雅上月起被延長試用期120日，並且重啟有關投訴她的調查。利君雅試用期至今至被延長47天，尚餘72日。《蘋果》獲悉，港台行政部正協助副廣播處長馮建業處理調查工作。早前調查小組曾要求負責處理投訴的「機構傳訊及節目標準組」，遞交部份涉及當事人的投訴資料詳情，但無一併索取涉及利君雅的讚賞資料，被質疑對利君雅不公。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，利君雅事件曝光後，馮建業要求傳訊及節目標準組，將涉及當事人的所有投訴悉數列印遞交，數量超過3,000宗。雖然馮建業曾在員工大會承諾會一併考慮對利君雅的讚賞，但據悉，行政部並無索取相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麥麗貞今向申訴署投訴失當<br />\n<br />\n港台工會則表示，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a87b22eb34d4ba0bdd34c1bfb7a8733d01d3ca52","tid":2294390,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"香港人真係抵撚死<br />\n一個唔同血統都企得咁前<br />\n其他所謂香港人既記者做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}